description: RDE, Inc. owns and operates Restaurant.com. The company operates Restaurant.com, a restaurant deal space that connects digital consumers, businesses, and communities offering approximately 200,000 dining and merchant deal options nationwide at 182,500 restaurants and retailers to 7.8 million customers. It sells discount certificates for restaurants and complementary entertainment and travel offerings and consumer products on behalf of third-party merchants. The company is based in Norcross, Georgia.
